import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Box } from '../../lib'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"box"}}>{`Box`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Hello, I'm a mdx file!`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" />`} __scope={{props,Box}}><Box background="#CCC" width="100px" height="100px" /></Playground>
<PropsTable of={Box} /></MDXTag>
